nce\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading The Royal Agricultural Society of Queensland in consultation with Equestrian Queensland, Toowoomba Regional Council and other industry stakeholders, has identified an opportunity to build an equestrian centre of excellence at Toowoomba Showgrounds.\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 482, \"end\": 492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"score\": 0.9989464999981433, \"rank\": 0.0010546110323163998, \"text\": \"Queensland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\"}, {\"begin\": 494, \"end\": 520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toowoomba_Region\", \"score\": 0.996802901544935, \"rank\": 0.003207352677243272, \"text\": \"Toowoomba Regional Council\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toowoomba_Region\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toowoomba_Region\"}, {\"begin\": 596, \"end\": 613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_facility\", \"score\": 0.7756906549752044, \"rank\": 0.28917371066184466, \"text\": \"equestrian centre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_facility\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_facility\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Loginor\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"The Royal Agricultural Society\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"Queensland\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"consultation\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"other industry stakeholders\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"Toowoomba Showgrounds\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RASQ CEO Damon Philips said that once developed it could host large scale equestrian events of high standard, fit-for-discipline competition surfaces.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 664, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Damon\", \"score\": 0.9955938881635228, \"rank\": 0.0041170254559637015, \"text\": \"Damon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Damon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Damon\"}, {\"begin\": 670, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philips\", \"score\": 0.9999999919878064, \"rank\": 5.6713255712049085e-09, \"text\": \"Philips\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philips\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philips\"}, {\"begin\": 729, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9993497485844415, \"rank\": 0.0006506419713737443, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"discipline\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These improvements would fill an identified gap in the Queensland equestrian facility market, in both the short and long term,\\\" Mr Phillips said.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"score\": 0.9989464999981433, \"rank\": 0.0010546110323163998, \"text\": \"Queensland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These improvements\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"an identified gap\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"both the short and long term\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr Phillips\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said the RASQ has co